original_title: Abbott and Costello Meet Jerry Seinfeld
overview: This is an important documentary done by a great fan of Abbott and Costello - Jerry Seinfeld. This portrait of Abbott and Costello is one of the best put to film. It does more than just play clips or just pay homage to them. Seinfeld found the things that inspired them to start with.
title: Abbott and Costello Meet Jerry Seinfeld
